  "title": "fix(connectNumericMenu + connectRange): stop sending invalid clickedFilters event",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\nJIRA: [FX-1633](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-1633)\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nThe [Clicked Filters](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/api-methods/clicked-filters/) method of Insights does not support numeric filters, but the `connectNumericMenu` and `connectRange` connectors still send this event automatically when refined. This generates errors on the dashboard's events debugger (see [CR-1588](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/CR-1588)).\r\n\r\nThis PR removes this call.\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\nThe `clickedFilters` event is not sent anymore during the lifecycle of the widget using the underlying `connectNumericMenu` and `connectRange` connectors.",
